## Development

```bash
npm install
npm run dev          # Start dev server with HMR (Chrome)
npm run dev:firefox  # Start dev server for Firefox
```

Load the extension from `dist/chrome/` (or `dist/firefox/`).

## Build

```bash
npm run build      # Production build for all browsers
npm run package    # Create .zip files for store submission
```

## Testing

```bash
npm test           # Run tests
npm run typecheck  # Type checking
```
